reviewText:
- not optimized;
- can crash or freeze at any random point;
- so many bugs I gave up counting;
- no widescreen support;

Barely playable at all because of severe bugs and glitches. This game shouldn't been released to Steam. Let it rest as another low (or zero) budged FPS from the 00's. I gave it a try, I did not enjoy it at all. :)
